item.title: CVE-2019-5492|2024-08-04T19:54:53.568Z -- netapp%2C%20inc. -- element%20plug-in%20for%20vcenter%20server
item.description: Element Plug-in for vCenter Server versions prior to 4.2.3 may disclose sensitive account information to an unauthenticated attacker. NetApp HCI Compute Node versions prior to 1.4P2 bundle affected versions of Element Plug-in for vCenter Server.
